ViennaNGS version 0.03
======================

ViennaNGS is a collection of Perl Modules for Next-Generation Sequencng (NGS) analysis.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Bio::Perl
  Bio::DB::Sam (requires samtools)
  File::Basename
  File::Temp

